<span style="font-weight: bold;">Collecting Gold Cards</span> <br>
    Collecting Gold Cards is as easy as taking a seat at any stake or level of Jetbull's real money ring game. It's essential to learn about Gold Cards to devise your redemption strategy and ensure you get the best value for your reward collection. <br>
    <br>
    <span style="font-weight: bold;">How do I earn a Gold Card?</span> <br>
    As long as you are playing in the real money ring games, you can receive a gold card. Even when you fold your hands, you still have the chance to get a Gold Card since there is no special requirement about acquiring a Gold Card.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; <br>
    <br>
    <span style="font-weight: bold;">How does it work?</span> <br>
    A Gold Card is released every time the table reaches a pre-determined rake amount. Therefore, you will see Gold Cards more frequently at the higher limit tables (even though you can earn gold cards at any stake level). When you earn a Gold Card, you'll see it move towards your spot at the table. <br>
    <br>
    <span style="font-weight: bold;">What is the value of a Gold Card?</span> <br>
    Obviously the value of the card depends on how you use them. Some players prefer to collect them in order to hit the juicy jackpot - $52,000, others might want to use them for tournaments buy-ins or cash rewards. Here is some information about the value of the Gold Cards, read them carefully: &nbsp; <br>
    <br>
    <span style="font-weight: bold;">Gold Card</span> <br>
    In a regular deck of cards, each individual card holds a different value based on its number or face, and its suit; Gold Cards are no different. <br>
    <br>
    <span style="font-weight: bold;">GOLD SERIES</span> <br>
    On the bottom right hand side of each Gold Card, you'll see a banner indicating a Series number. Hence you know which kind of series you are now participating. <br>
    <br>
    <span style="font-weight: bold;">Where can I view my Gold Cards?</span> <br>
    Gold Cards are saved in your Jetbull reward portfolio. When you log in to your accounts at Jetbull, you can find your personal Gold Cards collection simply by clicking the 'Rewards' tab. <br>
    <br>
    <span style="font-weight: bold;">Do Gold Cards expire?</span> <br>
    Do not worry! They never expire, like you are holding antiques, the longer you hold them, more value you get from them! <br>
